<author>tryz ạlṭfl yswʿ, jạn k jyạnạdạ</author>
<title>yswʿ ạ̉nt ạ̹lhy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- yswʿ ạ̉nt ạ̹lhy ḥbũk sẖạfy ạlwḥyd
 ạ̉nt ḥbyb nfsy ạ̉bdaⁿạ yswʿ ạ̉nt mn ạ̉ryd
 1- ạ̉sjd ạ̉mạmk ạ̹lhy ạ̉ʿtrf bk mlky
 hạ hy ḥyạty fy ydyk ạ̹fʿl bhạ mạ tryd
 2- tʿạl wạ̉mlk ʿly̱ qlby ạ̉twq ạ̹lyk tʿạl
 trñm lk sẖftạy ạ̉ḥbk llạ̉bdy
 3- tnḥny lạ̹smk kl rkbẗ wyʿtrf kl lsạn
 ạ̹smk yswʿ kẖlạṣy ạ̉rddh fy kl ḥyn</lyrics>
</song>